{"tid":1243130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你或者身邊既人仲諗緊620、621好唔好出黎...請入一入黎","createTime":"2019-06-19T10:27:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T09:09:18.000Z","uid":188828,"like":153,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"d36d05160911995df9de453c19a78c92d0974334","tid":1243130,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:27:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yppJ4jh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyppJ4jh.png&h=6d18deae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eadbtL3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeadbtL3.png&h=1c92a7b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ro0X8L9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fro0X8L9.png&h=05f5b4a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人<br />\n我唔知你睇到上面嗰三張相有咩感受<br />\n呢三張係黎自國際特赦組織 (紐西蘭) 的廣告<br />\n講緊既係 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「沉默即是幫兇」</span></span><br />\n今日無意中見到呢三張相<br />\n我心情好沉重<br />\n過往自己既沉默究竟令幾多人負上咗代價？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日立法會直播 鼠王芬又黎話<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>代表沉默的大眾</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n點解政府會覺得即使有二百萬人行出黎<br />\n仍然有五百個人支持緊佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n現實就係咁<br />\n你<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">一日唔行出黎</span></span> 你<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">一日都會俾施暴者當做支持佢既勢力</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">最暴力既從來唔係睇得見既暴力</span><br />\n<br />\n我唔理你<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非定勇武定中立</span></span>都好<br />\n620 621 甚至往後既日子<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">冇人能夠代表你 除咗你自己</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我要講既<br />\n上面三張圖講晒<br />\n<br />\n歡迎各位廣傳俾所謂既中立人士/仲諗緊要唔要企出黎既人<br />\n呢場仗未打完！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tcWsMDp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtcWsMDp.png&h=0390fef2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca9c09ae13b269d4e1ee1d8abc23e30d571b15ab","tid":1243130,"uid":188828,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:28:23.000Z","msg":"*五百萬人 先岩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 手快快打錯"},{"pid":"776d91a5668752369d84e33dbcbf66a07c265d64","tid":1243130,"uid":156936,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:39:16.000Z","msg":"各位好 阻阻大家<br />\n夢見好多人想開放日遊覽禮賓府。<br />\n但聽聞條斜路好危險，驚人多出現意外。<br />\n為安全著想，出席任何活動前，<span style=\"color: red;\">大家都有義務了解該地環境</span>，<br />\n希望各位唔好一知半解的情況下跟隨人流，造成危險。<br />\n===============<br />\n建議巴士路線及巴士站<br />\n===============<br />\n【新巴】13 旭龢道 - 中環（大會堂）23B 寶馬山 - 羅便臣道<br />\n【城巴】40M 華富（北） - 金鐘（政府總部）<br />\n【九巴】103 竹園邨 - 蒲飛路<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pZoOuRy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpZoOuRy.jpg&h=6ca9e50d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5v6z9Rz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5v6z9Rz.jpg&h=7291e991&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n===============<br />\n建議地鐵步行路線<br />\n===============<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JUqEBwz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJUqEBwz.jpg&h=f978913f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n===============================<br />\n禮賓府高空、地則及2018香港地圖懶人包<br />\n===============================<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QEDVUie.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQEDVUie.jpg&h=db80f34f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YFueqpV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYFueqpV.jpg&h=2680d5df&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bc0tuRA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbc0tuRA.jpg&h=7815bbe6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zeyZBwz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzeyZBwz.jpg&h=6ed57e57&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n===============<br />\n禮賓府地下通道新聞<br />\n===============<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ceZBDKW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FceZBDKW.jpg&h=7ac3a5fb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主現時收集以下的資料及圖片，作學術研究之用 :<br />\n1. 禮賓府正確的出入口和閘門總數<br />\n2. 禮賓府旁舊樓梯及非行車小徑等Google Map無法標示之通道<br />\n3. 急救站、飲水機、洗手間或可設立急救站空地等休息位置<br />\n4. 野生犬隻出沒或聚居地點 (可以Google map mark比我最好)<br />\n5. 由蘭桂坊或香港動植物公園前往的最佳路線<br />\n<br />\n歡迎加入討論: <strong>圖解香港禮賓府旅遊路線</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241712/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241712/page/1</a><br />\n更多細節請用追故模式<br />\n<br />\n最後，禮賓府係法定古蹟，落成年份為1851年，相當有歷史價值，係一家大細親子好去處，大家記得要遵守秩序，<span style=\"color: red;\">去之前記得做足功課</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等每年既開放日一到就一齊去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />平時無開放千奇唔好去呀"},{"pid":"f72b6e2340b4dd3fdbad926a8b7246a48ae92b0b","tid":1243130,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:47:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"daffe44aa2f00fefc242cb54da2fa9493c4820d2","tid":1243130,"uid":87901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:49:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"840bc85fd8c50d312b2a7d8e3d4c79e1862cde77","tid":1243130,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:51:17.000Z","msg":"[深度分析]香港人的抗爭理念<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1241532\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1241532</a><br />\n推"},{"pid":"e951cf8a147444569263d5781d0b703ce93f567f","tid":1243130,"uid":83785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:53:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"567e5910cd8ac684f65fd0076442d64e2bfcb47a","tid":1243130,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:06:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d18e935afc99d75368f85878978470d8c1880ff7","tid":1243130,"uid":71960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:14:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df4e49db3a3d3e3526b596d48b1316febcca016f","tid":1243130,"uid":161436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:29:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「沉默即是幫兇」</span></span>"},{"pid":"2fb47ca5d5e2f3f18496807e794d212946531522","tid":1243130,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:29:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1409877577363c2053f4889c5359e760ede8c34a","tid":1243130,"uid":161436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df4e49db3a3d3e3526b596d48b1316febcca016f","tid":1243130,"uid":161436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:29:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「沉默即是幫兇」</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:29:24.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"731b46d35e23791eeb52f5faeaad14b615f44606","tid":1243130,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:29:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"11035f123236623b3bc39fb54c7406bd4f5cbefa","tid":1243130,"uid":126678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:33:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"735951261ed60e4268eab3aabfcbb722a6ed00a0","tid":1243130,"uid